<br>
I come seeking advice...<br>
<br>
1) Any good pally websites/boards out there?<br>
<br>
2) Weapons weapons weapons-- and more weapons!!  I am currently 52nd season and using two weapons depending on the situation.  Mostly have questions about my 2h.<br>
-------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
2hs<br>
Natures Defender  <br>
Damage: 38 Delay: 46 <br>
AC: +45 Str: +10 Dex: +10 Wis: +10 Disease Resist: +15 Poison Resist: +15 HP: +25 Mana: +25  <br>
Weapon Skill: Two Hand Slash <br>
