<br>
Curious as to why nobody mentioned the Greatstaff of the Four winds, they run about 80k with a very nice ratio 41 dmg 31 dly with a 75 DD and +125 HP with resists. Is that not a good choice?<br>
<br>
Also the Lance of the Flame Knight looks pretty good-- although it runs a bit higher (200k OUCH!)<br>
<br>
I have considered Primal as well, but they seem fairly rare in bazaar lately as most guilds have been neglecting Sleeper's.<br>
<br>
<br>
